data.description: **All New Carpeting on the First Floor on 10/16/2023!** Welcome to this very nice 3 bed, 2 bath home with a bonus room upstairs, 2027 sqft and located minutes from Tinker AFB. This property offers a fantastic opportunity for comfortable living and versatile use of space! With an open kitchen and walk in pantry right next to the dinette perfect for entertaining guests. There is also a large shed out doors for a shop or storage and no HOA & they allow CHICKENS! This home offers convenience for military personnel or professionals working at the base.
